# GHZ state — three-qubit maximal entanglement.
#
# A chain of CNOTs spreads q0's superposition across all three qubits, giving
# (|000> + |111>)/sqrt(2). All three measurements are perfectly correlated: the
# outcome is always 000 or 111, each with probability 1/2.
qubits 3

H q0
CNOT q0 q1
CNOT q1 q2

MEASURE q0
MEASURE q1
MEASURE q2
